        Creating an event with an event ID, associated user name, person's ID, latitude and longitude, country, city, year, and the type of the event
        Parameters:
        eventID - the unique ID for the event
        associatedUserName - the username to which the person belongs to
        personID - the ID of the person which the event belongs to
        latitude - the latitude of the event's location
        longitude - the longitude of the event's location
        country - the country in which the event occurred
        city - the city in which the event occurred
        eventType - the type of the event
        year - the year in which the event occurred
